translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior3_1b132f56:
    # "Did Vaelen not see it, she wondered, or did he not want to see it? Did he not care?"
    ""

translate ru TheHollowWorldWarrior3_b2c47a9b:
    # "Sarah wished she knew the answer to any of it. Instead, she merely excercised control over what little she could affect, and instructed the men on rebuilding the wagons."
